        "data_description": {
          "push_twist_mode": "Controls the behavior when holding the button and twisting. Default mode shows two sliders (twist position and push-twist position) that clamp at boundaries. Continuous mode is like default but wraps around instead of clamping. Selector mode shows 12 per-slot sliders, enables click and double-click events, and shows the selected slot entity."
